<p>I want to create a script that takes the <code>telephoneNumber</code> attribute from Active Directory and inserts the value into an existing XML file. What I have is code to retrieve the attribute from AD:</p>  <pre class="lang-vb prettyprint-override"><code>Set objSysInfo = CreateObject("ADSystemInfo") strUser = objSysInfo.UserName  Set objUser = GetObject("LDAP://" &amp; strUser) WScript.Echo "" &amp; objUser.telephoneNumber </code></pre>  <p>Now I need to take this result and insert it in specific locations (everywhere 101 is writing). How can I do this?</p>